title: "Astronomers are very excited" about UFO files, cosmologist says
description: President Trump has ordered the release of all government documents related to aliens, UFOs and extraterrestrial life. It comes after former President Barack Obama addressed the topic earlier this week and said aliens are real, a statement which he later modified. CBS News' Ed O'Keefe reports, and contributor Janna Levin has more details.

title: What might we learn from UFO files Trump told the government to release?
description: President Trump said he's directing the Pentagon and other federal agencies to identify and release files related to UFOs and extraterrestrial life.
